Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.21,0:19:40.95,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙  雙  雙鑽頭…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.19,0:19:42.82,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙雙雙雙雙鑽頭…
